headline: CrowdStrike Appoints Brad Burns as Chief Communications Officer
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, May 13, 2025--CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced the appointment of Brad Burns as chief communications officer (CCO). Burns will lead the company’s global communications strategy, supporting executive leadership as CrowdStrike accelerates its growth and scale as cybersecurity’s platform innovator for the AI era.
